Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:03.56,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,boku wa dokomade chikazuketandarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:08.85,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,juunengo no mirai kagayaiteru sugata wa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:15.36,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,koukai wa shinai jibun de egaita story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:21.99,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,fumidaseba yukute habamu genjitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:28.33,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}makenai to ima mune ni chikatta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:37.05,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kokorozashita tsukamitai yume ga arukara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:43.30,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,moyashite yuke jounetsu wo atsuku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:50.06,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,yume no tochuu de meguriau deai to wakare
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:56.32,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kimi ga oshietekureta boku dake ga motsu chikara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:03:02.20,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,tachiagatteikundayo nando tsumazuitatte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.45,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,Dream of Life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:57.30,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:03.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:08.85,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:15.36,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:21.99,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:28.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:37.05,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:43.30,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:50.06,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:56.32,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:03:02.20,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And rise back up again and again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:54.47,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,kurikaesu nibuku detarame na sekai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:23:00.40,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,urusakute mimi wo fusaida
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:07.65,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,nan no tame ni kizutsukeatteiru no?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.49,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,Can you hear my heartbeat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:14.99,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,Baby I trust you my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:18.96,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,zetsubou ni fushita kokoro no sumi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.67,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,orikasanaru mujun no kage ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:25.55,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,mune wo itamenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.55,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,ashita wo yume mireru no?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:35.56,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,toori ame no ato ni mitsuketa niji wo omotte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:42.19,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,me wo tojiru Fly with me donna nagai yume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:45.65,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,iroasenai kimi to nara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:50.95,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,egakidaseru kienai niji mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:58.91,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,deaeta ano hi ni mita tsukiakari de sae mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:05.88,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,utsushidasu nando demo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:10.30,Lyrics-Jap-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,950)}nando demo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:54.47,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In this world, every day is dull and full of nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:23:00.40,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cover my ears, trying to mute the noise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:07.65,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do people hurt each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:18.96,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the contradictory, overlapping shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.67,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the recesses of my heart, fallen into despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:25.55,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While carrying this pain in my chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.55,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,can I really dream of tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:35.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remembering the rainbow I found after the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:42.19,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I close my eyes; come fly with me into my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:45.65,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I have you, who shines so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:50.95,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can envision an everlasting rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:58.91,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And even remember the moonlight of night we met
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:05.88,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can picture them... countless times
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:10.30,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,950)}over and over again
